name: THE OCULUS
description:
The Oculus is a teleportation gate to Novus Planet 126 light years from earth. The Oculus is guarded by a shaman and can only be used at certain time, in order to use this portal we should make an agreement that used by user's soul as payment.

The content of that agreement is that we cannot bring (animals, plants, rocks or anything) on the return to earth, if we did it our souls would be sealed and unable to return to earth.

To get through the portal we have to go through the spell "advenio adeo facio" which means "to come visit to experience."
